snippet.title: The Midnight Janitor Tales | Game Trailer | Browser
snippet.description:
#3DHorror #RetroHorror #Bitsy3D #3DFPS #Bitsy #InteractiveFiction #horrorgame #FPShorror

Play Midnight on (Browser Game): https://cultbalmproductions.itch.io/the-midnight-janitor-tales

Based on the 'Creepy Public Toilet Woman' creepypasta (Read it here: https://urbanfright.blogspot.com/2021/10/sightings-of-strange-figure-near-public.html), an interactive fiction game in the style of retro horror games.

You play as Christopher the janitor and try to end your night shift while you avoid the entities that may end your life So get ready to step into the world of chaos and riddles.

CCTV Ghost Image Credits: UpTown PRANK (アップタウン本部 (@uptownch))

Follow:
Itch - https://cultbalmproductions.itch.io/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/BalmCult
